### Get all products
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/Product/Products
Accept: application/json

### Get product by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/Product/69e39116a24345c4aef8ad62
Accept: application/json

### Get products by name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/Product/ExampleProductName
Accept: application/json

### Get products by category
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/Product/GetProductsByCategory/electronics
Accept: application/json

### Create a new product
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/Product
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "60f7ebf53642a928ffec7f15",
  "name": "New Product",
  "category": "electronics",
  "price": 199.99
}

### Update a product
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/Product/60f7ebf53642a928ffec7f15
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "60f7ebf53642a928ffec7f15",
  "name": "Updated Product",
  "category": "electronics",
  "price": 249.99
}

### Delete a product
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/Product/69e39116a24345c4aef8ad62
